<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Event Reminder</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc107 0%, #ff8f00 100%); color: #333; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .event-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc107 0%, #ff8f00 100%); color: #333; border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin: 25px 0; text-align: center; }
        .countdown { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin: 15px 0; }
        .checklist { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0; }
        .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; }
        @media (max-width: 600px) { .container { margin: 0 10px; } .content, .header { padding: 20px 15px; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>⏰ Event Reminder</h1>
        <p>Don't forget about your upcoming event!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hi {{userName}},</h2>
        <p>This is a friendly reminder that your event is coming up soon!</p>

        <div class="event-card">
            <h3 style="font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px;">{{eventName}}</h3>
            <div class="countdown">🕐 Tomorrow!</div>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 10px 0;">📅 {{formatDate eventDate}}</p>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 10px 0;">📍 {{venue}}</p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin: 10px 0;">🎫 {{ticketCount}} ticket{{#if (gt ticketCount 1)}}s{{/if}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="checklist">
            <h3>✅ Pre-Event Checklist:</h3>
            <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 15px;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">📱 Have your ticket QR codes ready (check your email)</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">🆔 Bring a valid photo ID if required</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">🚗 Plan your transportation and parking</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">🌤️ Check the weather forecast</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">💧 Stay hydrated and bring water if allowed</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">📞 Save our support number: (555) 123-4567</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #e7f3ff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
            <h4>🎉 Get Ready to Have Fun!</h4>
            <p>We're excited that you'll be joining us tomorrow! Make sure to arrive at least 30 minutes early to avoid any last-minute rush.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <p>Need to view your tickets again?</p>
            <a href="#" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 25px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc107 0%, #ff8f00 100%); color: #333; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: bold; margin: 15px 0;">View My Tickets</a>
        </div>

        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team. Have an amazing time at the event!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 EventHub. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Event Support: <a href="mailto:support@eventhub.com">support@eventhub.com</a> | (555) 123-4567</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>